  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Suzaku Clan, Level 4+</p><p>Through extensive experimentation, you've learned how to control and tailor the ebb and flow of water release to better suit your style. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>You can now learn and use ninjutsu with the water release keyword.</li><li>Whenever you use a ninjutsu with the water release keyword, you may add the Fire Release Keyword to it and convert half the damage dealt if any to fire. You may only use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus per long rest.</li><li>You cannot take the Gale Force Feat.</li></ul>",
